2026-04-16 21:23:04 - llm.aliyun_llm - INFO - 收到 LLM API 响应  result={'choices': [{'message': {'content': '我是 PM（产品经理）数字员工，收到指令后需要按工作规范处理任务。让我按步骤执行：\n\n**Step 1 — 读取邮箱**', 'reasoning_content': "Let me understand my role and task:\n\n1. I am a PM (Product Manager) digital employee\n2. I need to check my mailbox for task_assign messages\n3. If there's a task, I need to follow the workflow: read mail → load product design spec → read requirements → write product spec → write to shared workspace → notify Manager → mark message done\n\nLet me start by checking my mailbox.", 'role': 'assistant', 'tool_calls': [{'function': {'arguments': '{"skill_name": "mailbox", "task_context": "读取 PM 邮箱，检查是否有 task_assign 类型的任务邮件。需要执行：python3 /workspace/skills/mailbox/scripts/mailbox_cli.py read --mailboxes-dir /mnt/shared/mailboxes --role pm"}', 'name': 'skill_loader'}, 'id': 'tool-88dd1c84b6d34a7a80f60b595768c2e2', 'index': 0, 'type': 'function'}]}, 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'index': 0, 'logprobs': None}], 'object': 'chat.completion', 'usage': {'prompt_tokens': 4070, 'completion_tokens': 181, 'total_tokens': 4251, 'completion_tokens_details': {'reasoning_tokens': 84}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 0}}, 'created': 1776345784, 'system_fingerprint': None, 'model': 'glm-5.1', 'id': 'chatcmpl-c9f8e7db-e908-902b-a662-674f7e41d9b8'}
